+## Overview
+
+Total revenue across all orders was $7,154.44, from 30 orders placed between May 2 and May 21, 2026.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget led with $2,392.00 in revenue, followed by Widget at $2,118.94. Doohickey earned $1,513.00 and Sprocket $1,130.50. Gadget's lead stems from its high unit price despite low volume.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North topped regions at $2,176.35, ahead of East ($1,830.79) and South ($1,732.48). West trailed at $1,414.82, roughly 65% of North's total.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Prioritize Gadget stock: it generates the highest revenue ($2,392.00) on low unit counts.
+- Grow West sales, the weakest region at $1,414.82, to close the gap with North.
+- Bundle Sprocket, the lowest-revenue product at $1,130.50, with stronger sellers.
